contentfulPagePressRelease.title: Qatar Foundation’s National Sport Day Instagram Competition

childMarkdownRemark.html:
On 10 February, QF celebrated National Sport Day with lots of fun, athletic challenges and activities for the community to enjoy.

If you attended any of the activities and captured a great moment, share your photos with us on Instagram for a chance to win an amazing prize.

All you have to do is:

  1. Post one photo on your Instagram from our various National Sport Day venues around the QF campus
  2. Use #QF_NSD to enter the competition

    The competition will be ending on 13 February at 11:59 pm.

    The best photo will be handpicked by QF and the winner announced on 16 February at 16:00.

    Good luck to all!
